{"id":129731,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/12/让子弹飞/","date":"2010-12-22T00:40:20Z","modified":"2015-07-12T23:20:16Z","title":"【真理部】让子弹飞","content":"<p>广电总局紧急通知：因为设计敏感话题，请全国12月22日起减少《让子弹飞》排片场次。与《非诚勿扰2》排片比为《让》3：7《非》。并且减少宣传本片，减少话题舆论。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2010/12/Screen-shot-2010-12-23-at-3.32.01-PM.png\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2010/12/Screen-shot-2010-12-23-at-3.32.01-PM.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"Screen shot 2010-12-23 at 3.32.01 PM\" width=\"398\" height=\"247\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129732\" /></a></p>\n<p>【“真理部”是网民对中国共产党中央委员会宣传部和其下属的各省宣传部，以及国家级的国务院新闻办公室，中央文明办，国家广播电影电视总局，出版总署，文化部等一系列言论出版审查机构的总称。】</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/05/zhenlibu.jpg\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/05/zhenlibu.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"zhenlibu\" width=\"550\" height=\"120\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-149165\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/05/zhenlibu.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/05/zhenlibu-300x65.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>[图片来源：<a href=\"http://clickca.wordpress.com/\">百草园</a>]</p>\n","author":35,"categories":[8649],"tags":[9254,15248]}